dmca.title: Copyright
dmca.body:
o Whom It May Concern:

Please note that below-referenced copyright infringement notice does not
substantially comply with the required notification elements of the Digital
Millennium Copyright Act of 1998 ("DMCA").

Please note that we have not passed on the substantive merits of your claim.

Please visit our web site at www.theplanet.com/legal.
 
Legal Response Team
THEPLANET.COM INTERNET SERVICES, INC.

-----Original Message-----
From: ditt0bx@gmail.com [mailto:ditt0bx@gmail.com] On Behalf Of Emma
Dobrescu
Sent: Wednesday, January 25, 2006 9:07 AM
To: copyright@theplanet.com
Subject: Copyright

It has been brought to my attention that wobbilisim.com is a ripp-off of my
portfolio ( www.thinkpinkstudio.com ). I have tried to email the domain
owner at the email in the registrar's record and the email addresses
provided on his website, but all the emails came back to me with failed
delivery. I have tried to track the hosting company for that website but
have failed to do so as clientnshosting.net has no contact information.
However, in the traceroute I have encountered the reverse of theplanet.com.
Could you please tell me if wobbilisim.com is currently hosted by you and if
so, could you please ask your client to kindly remove the ripp-off
immediately so that he won't put himself  and you in an uncomfortable
situation?

Best regards,
Emma Dobrescu
